=<span style="font-family: 'Trebuchet MS',Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 160%;">GOOGLE Cr-48 CHROMEBOOK WIKI</span>= 

----
====The Cr-48 is an unbranded notebook computer designed by Google and manufactured by [[@http://www.inventec.com/english/indexEN.htm|Inventec]]. The Cr-48 was distributed by Google between December 2010 and April 2011 to participants in the [[http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-20024897-1.html|Chrome OS Pilot Program]].==== 
====Intended as a reference hardware design, these computers were not made available for sale to the general public. Approximately 60,000 Cr-48 notebooks were manufactured.==== 
====The guides provided here represent the distillation of work by numerous individuals. Original sources of information are noted in each guide.==== 

